title: Celtics Vibe Check and Observations With Jared Weiss | Weekends with Wos
description:
Wos sits down with Boston Celtics and NBA beat writer for ‘The Athletic,’ Jared Weiss, to discuss the Boston Celtics, the Ime Udoka scandal (1:52), the overall culture of the team (5:29), what their goals are looking like this season (19:26), and more!
Host: Wosyn Lambre
Guest: Jared Weiss
Producer: Jade Whaley
